{"word":"Ishmael","slug":"ishmael","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Ishmael</b> - (God shall hear), son of Abraham and Hagar<p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=16&verse=11'>Gen 16:11</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=17&verse=18'>Gen 17:18</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=21&verse=10'>Gen 21:10</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=21&verse=14'>Gen 21:14</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=21&verse=18'>Gen 21:18</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=21&verse=21'>Gen 21:21</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=25&verse=12'>Gen 25:12</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=7&chapter=8&verse=24'>Jdg 8:24</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=19&chapter=83&verse=6'>Psa 83:6</a><p/>--\"The Outcast\", Life Summarized<p/>--Born of a bigamous marriage, with a foreigner<p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=16&verse=2'>Gen 16:2-4</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=16&verse=15'>Gen 16:15</a><p/>--May have had childish dreams that he was to be the heir<p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=17&verse=18'>Ge 17:18</a><p/>--The real heir born<p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=21&verse=1'>Ge 21:1-7</a><p/>--Lacking prudence, mocked at the weaning-feast of his rival<p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=21&verse=9'>Ge 21:9</a><p/>Thus became an outcast<p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=21&verse=10'>Ge 21:10-14</a><p/>--A man of the desert<p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=21&verse=21'>Ge 21:21</a><p/>--Returned to attend the funeral of his father, Abraham<p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=25&verse=9'>Ge 25:9</a><p/>--Became the head of a great nation<p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=17&verse=20'>Gen 17:20</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=25&verse=12'>Gen 25:12-16</a>"}]}